[Student "S"]
{[show S]
[BID 1!H] [BID 4NT] [BID 6!H]
[show NS]
With eleven cards in the "round" suits SOUTH has a lot of playing strength. So when NORTH bids 
a Limit Raise in \Hs SOUTH wants to know about Aces.
 

 
RKCBlackwood tells him that NORTH has two Aces plus the trump Queen, so SOUTH can see that 6\H 
is practically a certainty.}


